---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const description = "Learn about The Desperado, the chess club of IISER Mohali, our story, and our convenors.";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description={description}>
  <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-bg border-b border-border">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 chess-pattern opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <span class="font-sans font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-gold mb-6">About Us</span>
      <h1 class="font-serif font-semibold text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] text-parchment tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.1] mb-12">
        The Desperado
      </h1>
      <div class="max-w-[70ch] text-left mx-auto space-y-6">
        <p class="font-body text-lg leading-[1.8] text-muted">
          The Desperado emerged from a shared passion for strategy, foresight, and the 64 squares. We are the chess community of the Indian Institute of Science Education and Research (IISER) Mohali, dedicated to bringing togther all the chess enthusiasts on the campus.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="font-serif italic text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gold border-l-2 border-gold-dim pl-6 py-2 my-10">
          "Chess is a war over the board. The object is to crush the opponent's mind."
           <footer class="font-sans text-sm text-muted mt-4">--Bobby Fischer</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="font-body text-lg leading-[1.8] text-muted">
          Our mission is to foster a culture of analytical thinking, resilience, and sportsmanship. We believe that the skills honed over the chessboard—patience, calculation, and grace under pressure—are invaluable both in science and in life. 
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-lg leading-[1.8] text-muted">
          From casual bullet games in the evening to intense inter-IISER classical battles, the club provides a space for everyone. We look forward to regularly organizing tournaments, workshops, and friendly matches, ensuring that every member has the opportunity to grow and enjoy the game.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

